Class Location

  • java.lang.Object
    • Location
  • public class Location
extends java.lang.Object
    The class location is also a very basic class that checks if the rows equal to the columns. Location just initilizes row and column and then checks whether they're equivalent to each other or not. Location also has a toString method. It works as any other basic string returner.
